(618, 'PUBLIKASI', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>DAFTAR MEDIA PUBLIKASI FAKULTAS TEKNIK UNIVERSITAS PGRI MADIUN</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>1. SET-UP</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/SET-UP\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&amp;id=1PXYg2MvhftbmDJAkyrY_pixnOhIRU8tP\" style=\"height:90%; width:50%\" /></a></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><em>Set-up</em></span> : Jurnal Keilmuan Teknik&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">is a scientific journal that publishes articles in the field of Chemical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Industrial Engineering, Informatics Engineering, Information System. It is a journal to encourage research publication to research scholars, academicians, professionals and student engaged in their respective field. This journal is published by&nbsp;</span><strong><a href=\"http://unipma.ac.id/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: maroon;\" target=\"_blank\">Universitas PGRI Madiun</a></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">&nbsp;in&nbsp;</span><strong>June</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><strong>December</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">.&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/doubleclick/index\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iTLPR8jaJLbZF3P58R5DKA3dt7PYGruh/view?usp=sharing\" /></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>2. DOUBLECLICK</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/doubleclick/index\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&amp;id=1iTLPR8jaJLbZF3P58R5DKA3dt7PYGruh\" style=\"height:80%; width:50%\" /></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><em><strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">DoubleClick</span> </strong></em><strong>:</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\"><strong>Journal of Computer and Information Technology</strong> with registered number E-ISSN:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://u.lipi.go.id/1491387027\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: steelblue; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; cursor: url(\">2579-5317</a><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">&nbsp; and P-ISSN:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://u.lipi.go.id/1555035712\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: steelblue; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; cursor: url(\">2685-2152</a><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">&nbsp;will publish in </span><span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>August</strong></span><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\"> and </span><span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>February</strong></span><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\"><strong>.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">Topic of the DoubleClick Journal :</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">1. Application of information technology (Software engineering, system design, geographic information system mapping area, multimedia, simulation technique, robotics)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">2. Development and empowerment of society or creative economy trough e-commerce)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">3. Development of learning media based on information technology</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">4. Information System</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>3. RESEARCH</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/RESEARCH\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&amp;id=1fiCdzB6TuAMYhMyhnmB-o6RJbnQydh6d\" style=\"height:80%; width:50%\" /></a></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">RESEARCH</span>&nbsp;</strong>is&nbsp;a scientific journal that publishes articles in the field of Computer, Information systems &amp; Technology Management.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Journal of Computer, Information System &amp; Technology Management</strong>&nbsp;has been registered with&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"http://issn.pdii.lipi.go.id/issn.cgi?daftar&amp;1519872221&amp;1&amp;&amp;\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\">Online ISSN:&nbsp;2615-7357</a>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<a href=\"http://issn.pdii.lipi.go.id/issn.cgi?daftar&amp;1519878573&amp;1&amp;&amp;\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\">Print ISSN: 2615-7233</a></strong>&nbsp;and published by&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#B22222\">Universitas PGRI Madiun</span></strong> in&nbsp;<a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/RESEARCH/about/editorialPolicies#custom-4\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\"><strong>April</strong></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/RESEARCH/about/editorialPolicies#custom-4\" style=\"color: navy; text-decoration-line: none;\"><strong>October</strong></a>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>4. KAIZEN</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/Kaizen\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&amp;id=1MHno8YT-vwMldQY_HocERCFQRr3Jfbea\" style=\"height:80%; width:50%\" /></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">KAIZEN</span>&nbsp;</strong>is a scientific journal that publishes articles in the field of Management Systems &amp; Industrial Engineering.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Management System &amp; Industrial Engineering Journal</strong>&nbsp;has been registered with&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">Online ISSN:&nbsp;2615-7357&nbsp;/&nbsp;Print ISSN: 2615-7233</span></strong>&nbsp;and published by&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#B22222\">Universitas PGRI Madiun</span></strong> in&nbsp;<strong>May</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>November</strong>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>5. CHEESA</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/cheesa\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&amp;id=1Xz89tYzVcn-W0VN6epLkqgPJK3rGaCWJ\" style=\"height:80%; width:50%\" /></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">CHEESA</span>: Chemical Engineering Research Articles&nbsp;</strong>(<strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">E-ISSN:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://issn.brin.go.id/terbit/detail/1517194447\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">2615-2347</span></a><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">, P-ISSN:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://issn.brin.go.id/terbit/detail/1517405275\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>2</strong>614-8757</span></a></strong>)&nbsp;is a scientific journal that publishes articles in the field of Chemical Engineering, and Chemistry. It is a journal to encourage research publication to research scholars, academicians, professionals and student engaged in their respective field. This journal is published by&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"http://unipma.ac.id/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\"><span style=\"color:#B22222\">Universitas PGRI Madiun</span></a></strong>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<strong>June</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>December</strong>. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">This journal has been accredited by National Journal Accreditation (ARJUNA) Managed by Ministry of Research, Technology, and Higher Education, Republic Indonesia with Third Grade (<strong><a href=\"https://sinta3.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/6672\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\">Sinta 3</a></strong>) since year 2018 to 2022 according to the&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1kOgdTBxiuO6wZMwo3QSqcur2YE5d6oHa/view?usp=sharing\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\">Decree No.&nbsp;85/M/KPT/2020</a>&nbsp;</strong>and<strong>&nbsp;</strong>reaccredited in&nbsp;3rd grade&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">(<a href=\"https://sinta3.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/6672\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: navy; cursor: url(\">Sinta 3</a>)&nbsp;since&nbsp;2021 to 2025.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>6. ELECTRA</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"http://e-journal.unipma.ac.id/index.php/electra\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&amp;id=1KHdIzCRIScjxPM3KpoCk7F8OKGt8Cud0\" style=\"height:80%; width:50%\" /></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">ELECTRA</span> : Electrical Engineering Articles</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(34, 34, 34)\">&nbsp;is scientific journal that publishes articles in the field of Electrical Engineering, Electronics, telecommunication, informatics, system engineering, Control System and Renewable Energy Application.