/a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://forms.gle/uU3DL526d4A32znd8\">SURVEI KEPUASAN</a></strong><a href=\"https://forms.gle/uU3DL526d4A32znd8\"><span style=\"color:rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family:docs-roboto; font-size:32px\">&nbsp;</span><strong>PENGGUNA&nbsp;</strong><strong>LULUSAN</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family:docs-roboto; font-size:32px\">&nbsp;</span><strong>FAKULTAS TEKNIK</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family:docs-roboto; font-size:32px\">&nbsp;</span><strong>UNIVERSITAS PGRI MADIUN</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '2023-02-16', 'Y', 0, 7, 'admin', 'f5', 5, 0, 0),
